abstract: Netherlands's Denk party is positioning itself as perhaps first pro-immigrant party in Europe, seeking to fight back against nativists and far-right candidates.

headline.print_headline: A Pro-Immigrant Party Rises in the Netherlands
headline.main: A Pro-Immigrant Party Rises in the Netherlands

snippet: Denk, or Think, is intended to attract minorities and represent their views in Dutch politics, where a right-wing anti-immigrant movement has caught fire....
lead_paragraph: Denk, or Think, is intended to attract minorities and represent their views in Dutch politics, where a right-wing anti-immigrant movement has caught fire.
